              <p class="text-body-color dark:text-dark-6"><strong>Business Nature:</strong> GenAI Solutions and Digital Services Provider</p>
              <p class="text-body-color dark:text-dark-6"><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://palportals.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">https://palportals.com</a></p>
              <p class="text-body-color dark:text-dark-6"><strong>Contact Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:legal@palportals.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">legal@palportals.com</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark dark:text-white mb-3">Jurisdiction:</h3>
            <p class="text-body-color dark:text-dark-6">
              This Website is operated from India and is subject to Indian laws. However, we serve clients globally, including the United States, United Kingdom, and European Union. This Legal Notice complies with applicable laws in these jurisdictions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2. Terms of Use -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark dark:text-white mb-4">2. Terms of Use</h2>
          
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark dark:text-white mb-3">2.1 License Grant</h3>
