              PAL Portals grants you a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable, and revocable license to access and use this Website for lawful purposes only. You may not modify, copy, distribute, transmit, display, perform, reproduce, publish, license, create derivative works from, transfer, or sell any information, software, products, or services obtained from this Website without our prior written consent.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark dark:text-white mb-3">2.2 Prohibited Uses</h3>
            <p class="text-body-color dark:text-dark-6 mb-3">You agree not to:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-body-color dark:text-dark-6 list-disc list-inside">
