              <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems or networks</li>
              <li>Introduce viruses, malware, or harmful code to our Website</li>
              <li>Engage in any form of automated data collection or scraping</li>
              <li>Reverse engineer, decompile, or attempt to derive source code</li>
              <li>Violate intellectual property rights of PAL Portals or third parties</li>
              <li>Use the Website for spamming, phishing, or other fraudulent activities</li>
              <li>Impersonate any person or entity</li>
              <li>Post obscene, defamatory, or inflammatory content</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark dark:text-white mb-3">2.3 User Accounts</h3>
            <p class="text-body-color dark:text-dark-6 mb-3">
